00:12:38,333 --> 00:12:41,125
You realize those are
your last words, right?

249
00:12:41,208 --> 00:12:44,208
'Cause even if we don't get you,
the cops sure will.

250
00:12:44,291 --> 00:12:46,541
Either way, your ass
is getting dragged to hell.

251
00:12:46,625 --> 00:12:48,500
-[gunshot]
-[yells]

252
00:12:52,083 --> 00:12:54,333
[thudding]

253
00:12:54,416 --> 00:12:55,875
[BOTH gasp]

254
00:12:55,958 --> 00:12:57,333
You think so, huh?

255
00:12:57,416 --> 00:12:59,541
Well, you won't be alive
to find out!

256
00:12:59,625 --> 00:13:01,291
[four gunshots]

257
00:13:01,375 --> 00:13:02,791
[grunts]

258
00:13:02,875 --> 00:13:05,791
[four gunshots]

259
00:13:05,875 --> 00:13:08,625
-[gunshots continue]
-[clicking]

260
00:13:08,708 --> 00:13:11,125
-[distant gunshots]
-Damn it.

261
00:13:11,208 --> 00:13:12,375
You're dead.

262
00:13:12,458 --> 00:13:14,458
-[gunshot]
-[yells, groans]

263
00:13:15,833 --> 00:13:18,208
[two gunshots]

264
00:13:18,291 --> 00:13:20,083
-[CHIKAI] Damn! Nice shot!
-[firing]

265
00:13:20,166 --> 00:13:21,875
-[shell casing clinks]
-[CHIKAI] Let's go!

266
00:13:24,500 --> 00:13:27,333
♪ I've got everything you need ♪

267
00:13:27,416 --> 00:13:30,041
[humming]

268
00:13:30,125 --> 00:13:32,333
Hey, sorry I'm so late!

269
00:13:32,416 --> 00:13:34,541
The good news is, I picked up
a bottle of wine

270
00:13:34,625 --> 00:13:36,000
and some of
your favorite pancakes

271
00:13:36,083 --> 00:13:38,083
on the way back, if you...

272
00:13:40,666 --> 00:13:44,083
[IMPERIAL BOSS]
Otter otter. Getting hotter.

273
00:13:45,583 --> 00:13:47,333
Mabu?

274
00:13:47,416 --> 00:13:51,166
[IMPERIAL BOSS] You look like
you're in "otter" agony, Mabu.

275
00:13:51,250 --> 00:13:54,791
[MABU]
Yes. I need you to service me.

276
00:13:54,875 --> 00:13:56,583
[IMPERIAL BOSS]
Oh, my.

277
00:13:56,666 --> 00:13:58,833
[chuckles]
As you wish, then.

278
00:13:58,916 --> 00:14:00,125
[hissing]

279
00:14:02,708 --> 00:14:04,958
[REO]
What's going on in there?

280
00:14:09,583 --> 00:14:11,333
You get away from Mabu!

281
00:14:11,416 --> 00:14:12,833
Reo.

282
00:14:12,916 --> 00:14:14,666
[grunts]
Bastard!

283
00:14:14,750 --> 00:14:16,500
What the hell
are you doing to him?

284
00:14:19,125 --> 00:14:20,833
You're me?

285
00:14:20,916 --> 00:14:22,541
[IMPERIAL BOSS]
Oh, hardly.

286
00:14:22,625 --> 00:14:24,416
I am an otter.

287
00:14:24,500 --> 00:14:26,625
Although I am you, as well,
in a sense.

288
00:14:26,708 --> 00:14:28,375
And what's that supposed
to mean?

289
00:14:28,458 --> 00:14:31,333
[IMPERIAL BOSS] You "otter" know
by now that my kind exist

290
00:14:31,416 --> 00:14:33,291
in this world as concepts.

291
00:14:33,375 --> 00:14:36,416
That is to say, I am a mirror
of the desires

292
00:14:36,500 --> 00:14:38,708
-in your heart.
-Don't touch him!

293
00:14:38,791 --> 00:14:40,666
[IMPERIAL BOSS] You're the one
who wants to make Mabu

294
00:14:40,750 --> 00:14:43,250
your possession. Not me, Reo.

295
00:14:43,333 --> 00:14:46,083
You're the one
who wants to lock lips

296
00:14:46,166 --> 00:14:48,125
with this hollow machine.

297
00:14:48,208 --> 00:14:49,500
You liar.

298
00:14:49,583 --> 00:14:51,958
[IMPERIAL BOSS]
"Disottersty" is not my policy.

299
00:14:52,041 --> 00:14:55,583
Your tangled strings are pulled
by your desires alone.

300
00:14:55,666 --> 00:14:57,291
Now, Mabu,

301
00:14:57,375 --> 00:15:00,583
why don't you tell us
who really matters to you?

302
00:15:00,666 --> 00:15:01,958
Is it him?

303
00:15:02,041 --> 00:15:03,666
Or is it me?

304
00:15:03,750 --> 00:15:06,666
Is there one of us
you can't live without?

305
00:15:06,750 --> 00:15:09,583
[MABU] I would fall to pieces
without your touch.

306
00:15:11,166 --> 00:15:13,458
I need you.

307
00:15:13,541 --> 00:15:15,625
-[shattering]
-[REO grunts]

308
00:15:15,708 --> 00:15:18,250
[REO] I knew you were nothing
but a fake.

309
00:15:18,333 --> 00:15:21,125
I was a fool for trusting you,
even for a second.

310
00:15:21,208 --> 00:15:22,958
I don't need either of you.

311
00:15:23,041 --> 00:15:26,583
I'll bring the real Mabu back,
with my own hands.

312
00:15:26,666 --> 00:15:28,416
One more.

313
00:15:28,500 --> 00:15:31,458
Just one more Dish of Hope.

314
00:15:34,750 --> 00:15:36,375
[HARUKA]
Kazu?

315
00:15:39,875 --> 00:15:41,875
[KAZUKI]
Sorry, did I wake you up?

316
00:15:41,958 --> 00:15:45,125
[HARUKA]
Are you sneaking out somewhere?

317
00:15:45,208 --> 00:15:47,416
[KAZUKI]
Yeah, kinda.

318
00:15:47,500 --> 00:15:51,041
[HARUKA] You weren't gonna
tell me this time either?

319
00:15:51,125 --> 00:15:53,958
You don't have to treat me
like a baby anymore.

320
00:15:55,000 --> 00:15:57,458
[KAZUKI]
You're right. I'm sorry.

321
00:15:57,541 --> 00:15:59,666
I'm leaving to go help Enta.

322
00:16:01,083 --> 00:16:02,958
[HARUKA]
Is it dangerous?

323
00:16:03,041 --> 00:16:06,541
[KAZUKI] Maybe, but I'm going
to give it my all.

324
00:16:06,625 --> 00:16:08,541
That's what he would do for me.

325
00:16:09,750 --> 00:16:11,958
Enta's a good friend to have.

326
00:16:12,041 --> 00:16:14,375
He was always there
for me, too, you know.

327
00:16:14,458 --> 00:16:17,833
When I was doing my rehab,
he came by every week.

328
00:16:17,916 --> 00:16:20,666
Hmm! Guess I should've been
paying closer attention.

329
00:16:20,750 --> 00:16:22,291
There's so much I missed.

330
00:16:22,375 --> 00:16:25,375
Me and Enta
both had the same wish.

331
00:16:25,458 --> 00:16:28,291
Here, I'll show you something
we made together.

332
00:16:30,500 --> 00:16:31,458
Huh?

333
00:16:32,916 --> 00:16:34,458
-[paper rustles]
-[gasps]

334
00:16:34,541 --> 00:16:36,750
And I just know
it'll come true.

335
00:16:36,833 --> 00:16:38,916
Cool, huh?

336
00:16:39,000 --> 00:16:41,250
-Is this me?
-Well, I...

337
00:16:41,333 --> 00:16:44,291
I think it's gonna be you.
Real soon.

338
00:16:44,375 --> 00:16:45,958
[gasps]

339
00:16:46,041 --> 00:16:48,458
[HARUKA] This guy was your
favorite player, right?

340
00:16:48,541 --> 00:16:50,208
And Enta's, too.

341
00:16:50,291 --> 00:16:52,250
[bubbling]

342
00:16:53,916 --> 00:16:56,333
[bubbling]

343
00:16:56,416 --> 00:16:58,333
[KAZUKI]
How could I forget?

344
00:16:58,416 --> 00:17:01,083
-[HARUKA laughs]
-[gasps]

345
00:17:01,166 --> 00:17:03,291
I love to watch you run.

346
00:17:03,375 --> 00:17:05,083
Come back soon.

347
00:17:07,500 --> 00:17:09,250
I'll be waiting.

348
00:17:09,333 --> 00:17:11,041
[KAZUKI]
Thank you.

349
00:17:12,041 --> 00:17:15,166
[panting]

350
00:17:15,250 --> 00:17:16,875
You only get one shot at life.

351
00:17:16,958 --> 00:17:20,500
No do-overs and no take-backs.

352
00:17:20,583 --> 00:17:23,625
When everything sucks,
you throw it all away!

353
00:17:23,708 --> 00:17:26,083
-[TOI] Chikai!
-[CHIKAI panting]

354
00:17:29,500 --> 00:17:32,875
[CHIKAI] Hey, you made it out
in one piece. That's good.

355
00:17:32,958 --> 00:17:34,583
[TOI]
Yeah.

356
00:17:34,666 --> 00:17:36,666
[CHIKAI] You wanna tell me
why you've still got that gun?

357
00:17:37,833 --> 00:17:39,833
[TOI]
I knew you would throw it away,

358
00:17:39,916 --> 00:17:41,583
so I swapped it out with a fake.

359
00:17:42,750 --> 00:17:44,166
[CHIKAI chuckles]

360
00:17:44,250 --> 00:17:45,666
[CHIKAI]
Nice one.

361
00:17:45,750 --> 00:17:47,875
That's my little brother
for you.

362
00:17:47,958 --> 00:17:49,416
[TOI]
I need to know.

363
00:17:49,500 --> 00:17:53,125
Are you planning
on throwing me away, too?

364
00:17:53,208 --> 00:17:57,333
I won't leave you. I don't care
if you're rotten to the core.

365
00:17:57,416 --> 00:17:59,083
You're my brother.

366
00:17:59,166 --> 00:18:00,916
And nothing
will ever change that.

367
00:18:01,000 --> 00:18:03,458
-[chuckles]
-[footsteps]

368
00:18:04,666 --> 00:18:07,666
You're a little too good to be
related to someone like me.

369
00:18:07,750 --> 00:18:09,666
And the bad guys...

370
00:18:09,750 --> 00:18:12,166
are the ones who survive
in this world, you know.

371
00:18:12,250 --> 00:18:13,416
[gasps]

372
00:18:13,500 --> 00:18:15,041
[gunshot]

373
00:19:49,916 --> 00:19:51,375
[dripping]

374
00:19:52,416 --> 00:19:53,625
[shudders]

375
00:19:53,708 --> 00:19:56,541
[CHIKAI groans]

376
00:19:58,125 --> 00:20:00,791
-Screw you!
-[gunshot]

377
00:20:00,875 --> 00:20:02,583
-[groaning]
-[thudding]

378
00:20:06,666 --> 00:20:08,625
[CHIKAI]
That asshole.

379
00:20:08,708 --> 00:20:11,375
[pained grunting]

380
00:20:12,416 --> 00:20:14,583
[gushing]

381
00:20:14,666 --> 00:20:16,333
[TOI]
What are you doing?

382
00:20:16,416 --> 00:20:19,916
We gotta get you
to a hospital right now!

383
00:20:20,000 --> 00:20:23,333
[CHIKAI] Don't bother.
Won't make any difference now.

384
00:20:26,875 --> 00:20:29,250
Chikai!

385
00:20:29,333 --> 00:20:31,416
[wheezing]

386
00:20:34,250 --> 00:20:36,291
-[grunts]
-[thudding]

387
00:20:36,375 --> 00:20:38,041
[grunts]

388
00:20:38,125 --> 00:20:40,750
[running footsteps]

389
00:20:40,833 --> 00:20:42,291
[CHIKAI chuckles]

390
00:20:42,375 --> 00:20:44,208
[CHIKAI]
I had everything.

391
00:20:44,291 --> 00:20:46,000
I had it all planned out.

392
00:20:46,083 --> 00:20:47,791
-Every last piece.
-You gotta stop talking.

393
00:20:47,875 --> 00:20:49,625
But then you screwed it up.

394
00:20:49,708 --> 00:20:51,833
Now look at how I ended up, huh?

395
00:20:51,916 --> 00:20:53,750
[TOI]
I'm sorry. So, please. Don't--

396
00:20:53,833 --> 00:20:56,125
[CHIKAI] That should be enough
money to feed you for a while.

397
00:20:56,208 --> 00:20:57,708
-[slaps]
-[TOI grunts]

398
00:20:59,500 --> 00:21:01,458
[CHIKAI]
Son of a bitch.

399
00:21:01,541 --> 00:21:04,333
It's all such a pain in the ass.

400
00:21:04,416 --> 00:21:06,916
Trying to connect to anyone.

401
00:21:10,375 --> 00:21:12,000
[shudders]

402
00:21:12,083 --> 00:21:13,333
[sobs]

403
00:21:13,416 --> 00:21:17,375
[wailing]

404
00:21:27,750 --> 00:21:31,750
♪

405
00:21:54,708 --> 00:21:59,375
♪

406
00:22:09,375 --> 00:22:12,375
♪

407
00:22:20,875 --> 00:22:23,875
♪

408
00:22:44,833 --> 00:22:46,916
[rustling]

409
00:22:48,375 --> 00:22:51,333
-Damn it!
-[fluttering]

410
00:22:54,375 --> 00:22:57,916
[wind rushing]

